{"Id":602248,"Title":"悯谗诗","Dynasty":"明","Author":"卢龙云","Context":"彼苍者天，照临下土。人之讹言，莫克先睹。断干单縻，沉舟积羽。野鸟为鸾，众言成虎。朝比埙篪，暮若仇虏。风运铅刀，雷鸣瓦釜。嗟彼谮人，德輶鲜举。惟谗罔极，百行胥愆。卒混苍素，莫辨媸妍。谓夷匪圣，谓蹠为贤。措躬无地，防口若川。于余何罪，视履则旋。中心自悼，顾影私怜。悲因抱玉，愁将绝弦。惟天之命，不爽其应。始以迹暌，终于实胜。金石难渝，姜桂有性。彼昏不知，具曰予圣。此道其常，厥惟天定。祸福由人，堪以自镜。君子闻言，靡惑于听。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"9847ef6763d6836aafb64036efe84461","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":7218076,"Sentence":"悲因抱玉，愁将绝弦。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bēi yīn bào yù ，chóu jiāng jué xián ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":13,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7218077,"Sentence":"惟天之命，不爽其应。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wéi tiān zhī mìng ，bú shuǎng jī yīng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":14,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7218078,"Sentence":"始以迹暌，终于实胜。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shi yi jì kuǐ ，zhōng yú shǐ shēng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":15,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7218079,"Sentence":"金石难渝，姜桂有性。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jīn dàn nán yú ，jiāng guì yǒu xìng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":16,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7218080,"Sentence":"彼昏不知，具曰予圣。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bi hūn bú zhī ，jù yuē yú shèng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":17,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7218081,"Sentence":"此道其常，厥惟天定。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"ci dāo jī cháng ，jué wéi tiān dìng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":18,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7218082,"Sentence":"祸福由人，堪以自镜。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huò fú yóu rén ，kān yi zì jìng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":19,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7218083,"Sentence":"君子闻言，靡惑于听。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jūn zi wén yán ，mǐ huò yú tīng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":20,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7218068,"Sentence":"风运铅刀，雷鸣瓦釜。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fēng yùn qiān dāo ，léi mǐng wǎ fǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null